  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Laboratory Analyst",
  "description": "<p><strong>Roles and Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Perform raw material, intermediate and final product Quality analysis</li>\n  <li>Interpret and report test results accurately and timely based on test method</li>\n  <li>Compliance to HSEQ systems requirement</li>\n  <li>Upkeep safety and quality standards, data integrity</li>\n  <li>Maintenance of equipment calibration</li>\n  <li>Manage and maintain chemicals, reagents and consumables, quality records</li>\n  <li>Chemical waste management according to regulatory requirements</li>\n  <li>Other work as assigned by Superior</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Our Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>NITEC/Diploma in Science related field</li>\n  <li>3-5years experience in analytical laboratory environment</li>\n  <li>Hands-on experience with analytical equipment and chemicals</li>\n  <li>Able to multi-task in a fast-paced environment</li>\n  <li>Meticulous to detail</li>\n  <li>Strong commitment to safety and quality</li>\n  <li>Experience with LIMS and SAP system is advantageous</li>\n</ul>",
